-- MOVES-Standard Chartered names Richard Pattle vice chairman, private banking clients
-- By Rama Venkat Raman in Bangalore
-- Thu Oct 02, 2014 04:59AM EDT
-- None



Oct 2 (Reuters) - Standard Chartered Plc <STAN.L> said it appointed Richard Pattle as vice chairman of private banking clients division.

Pattle is based in London, and leads Standard Chartered Private Bank's Ultra High Net Worth segment (UHNW) and focuses on client engagement initiatives. Pattle reports to Stephen Richards Evans, who is the global head of UHNW in the private banking clients arm.